// main.hexa — anima-agent service entry (target HEXA Mk.II+)
// Parallel channel bootstrap: Telegram + Discord + Web + CLI
//
// ── RISK AUDIT (Mk.II+ parse risk) ──────────────────────────────────
// CONFIRMED safe: effect, pure fn, ensures, comptime const,
//   async fn, select, spawn (green threads implemented)
// RISK: @intent(...)       → FALLBACK: verify block + comment
